node.text: the “papercuts” video is finally here. this video concept came from a dream I had a few months ago, when I woke up I wrote it all down immediately. a couple weeks later @machinegunkelly sent me this song and I knew exactly what I needed to do. this is my first rock video and a step into a new world. it was also a fucking honor to work with @travisbarker. I am beyond thankful for everyone involved in bringing this vision to life. directed & edited by me. DP - @franklinspov // 1st AC - @natalie_aa // production design - @fusinastudios // vfx - @scissorfilms // sfx makeup - @alanjmua // AD - @kelo_of_dopeness // bg wardrobe - @rasheedaameera // steadicam - @renardcheren // 3D animation - @kyleparnell // gaffer - @glowingambersproductions // casting - @milltickettv // producer - @saltarantino (rest of credits on youtube. enjoy ✌️)

node.text: toxicity video with @ytbtrench out now 🔓 the very first time I listened to this song I knew I wanted to do the video. I enjoyed making this piece - tapping into the realities of paranoia and distrust in today’s world. shot on 16mm film. special thank you to the legends @franklinspov & @allan_c_chavarria (all credits on youtube) love 🤞

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cole Bennett on August 04, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, camera and outdoors.

node.text: this photo is from 8 years ago. I had no idea the day I picked up a camera for the first time that it would change my life forever. I took a moment today to take it all in for the first time in a very long time. just wanted to say thank you and I love you all so much. keep going.. it’ll all be worth it, I promise.
